{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"aec05bd339","title":"满江红·庆祝我国第一次核试验成功","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"91d930597e","index":0,"year":1964,"month":10,"day":null,"articleId":"aec05bd339"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[{"id":"c2333145aa","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"千钧，表示极重。"},{"id":"fb9b65716f","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"庄生梦蝶，《庄子·齐物论》：“普者庄周梦为蝴蝶，棚棚然蝴蝶也。自喻适志与，不知周也。俄然觉，则然周也。意思是说，庄周作梦，梦见自己化为蝴蝶，自由飞翔，欣然自得，不知道自己是庄周。不久醒来，仍然是庄周。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6e99565382","type":"title","text":"满江红·庆祝我国第一次核试验成功","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339"},{"id":"c2333145aa","type":"paragraph","text":"小丑下台，","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339"},{"id":"fb9b65716f","type":"paragraph","text":"应欢送，","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339"},{"id":"75b93893cc","type":"paragraph","text":"礼炮轰隆。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339"},{"id":"c2dd546bde","type":"paragraph","text":"原子弹说爆就爆，","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339"},{"id":"2686be8870","type":"paragraph","text":"其乐无穷。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339"},{"id":"d6f99bbdfa","type":"paragraph","text":"十年丑史归尘土，","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339"},{"id":"0f9a0488e1","type":"paragraph","text":"一阵惊雷卷巨风。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339"},{"id":"1047aaba69","type":"paragraph","text":"笑老修大势去奖，","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339"},{"id":"0f5e842bac","type":"paragraph","text":"敲表钟。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339"},{"id":"04b4094d74","type":"paragraph","text":"忆往昔，","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339"},{"id":"191e06d1fc","type":"paragraph","text":"来势油；","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339"},{"id":"96716b770b","type":"paragraph","text":"众暖罗，","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339"},{"id":"b5319bdae9","type":"paragraph","text":"暗起哄。","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339"},{"id":"802155b3c8","type":"paragraph","text":"君不见，","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339"},{"id":"72349d0a4c","type":"paragraph","text":"人民自古是英雄。","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339"},{"id":"679669d9f8","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]十年丑史归尘土，1953年，斯大林逝世后，赫鲁晓夫任苏共中央第一书记，1958年兼任部长会议主席，1964年被迫辞职。十年是取其整数。楚臂挡车千钧力，庄生梦蝶一场空。看东方，火炬赤旗舞，万里红。","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339"}],"page":{"id":"7c3f0fd913","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"aec05bd339","start":235,"end":236}}}},"__N_SSG":true}